# Recommendation

## Recommended Solution

Deploy Prometheus Windows Exporter on all Windows Servers.

### Justification

* Simplest deployment model
* Lowest operational overhead
* Proven integration with SigNoz
* Successfully validated during testing
* Native support for Windows Service monitoring
* Easier troubleshooting and maintenance

### Standard Architecture

```text
Windows Server
    │
    ├── Windows Exporter
    │
    ▼
SigNoz OTel Collector
    ▼
SigNoz
```

