# Conclusion

Monitoring Windows Service status in SigNoz requires deployment of a data collection agent on the Windows server.

Two supported approaches exist:

1. Prometheus Windows Exporter (Recommended)
2. OpenTelemetry Collector Windows Service Monitoring

Based on testing performed, Windows Exporter is the preferred production solution due to simplicity, stability, lower operational overhead, and successful validation within the local test environment.

Approval is requested to deploy Windows Exporter on Windows servers requiring service-state monitoring and alerting within SigNoz.
